flowRoot.flowPara: openSUSE believes in choice and doesn't limit it. We also believe in making it easy for you to make decisions, and giving you the same seamless experience with openSUSE you'll get with any choices you make. We believe in adjusting your system to you, and no matter what route you take or what you try to achieve,
you're never alone with the openSUSE community. So make your choice, and choose openSUSE.
